<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5210543>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Pseudosteineria zhangi sp. nov. (A) Lateral view of male tail end, showing spicules, gubernaculum and caudal glands; (B) lateral view of female body, showing ovary, eggs and vulva; (C) lateral view of male anterior end, showing buccal cavity, amphid, cephalic setae and subcephalic setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5210543/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5210545>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Pseudosteineria zhangi sp. nov. (A) Lateral view of male anterior end, showing cephalic setae, buccal cavity and subcephalic setae; (B) lateral view of female anterior end, showing cephalic setae and subcephalic setae; (C) lateral view of male cloaca region, showing right spicule; (D) lateral view of male cloaca region, showing left spicule and apophysis of gubernaculum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5210545/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

